    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here's a revised draft that incorporates Marcus's passion for complex, technical challenges:\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nI wanted to personally reach out to you regarding the Senior Developer position at our Austin office. We were truly impressed by your technical skills and the enthusiasm you brought to our final interview. Your passion for tackling complex, legacy systems and deep dive problem solving is truly admirable, and we appreciate the time and effort you invested in sharing your experiences with us.\n\nUnfortunately, after careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate whose experience aligns more closely with our specific cloud architecture needs. Please know that this decision was not made lightly, and we were genuinely impressed by your qualifications and potential. You would be a great fit for many organizations, and we have no doubt that you will find a role that suits your skills and interests.\n\nWe appreciate the time and effort you invested in our interview process, and we're grateful for the opportunity to have met you. We wish you all the best in your job search and hope that our paths will cross again in the future.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n\nBy acknowledging Marcus's passion for complex, technical challenges, we're showing that we value his strengths and interests, even if the architecture fit wasn't quite there",
